Objective
 
The
 
goal
 
of

assignment

to
 
design
 
and
 
implement
 
an
 
AI-powered

efficiently
 
process
 
and
 
analyze
 
a

of
 
research
 
papers
 
in
 
PDF
 
format.

agent
 
should
 
be
 
capable
 
of
 
extracting
 
structured
 
information
 
from
 
these
 
documents
 
and
 
answering
 
complex
 
user
 
queries
 
based
 
on
 
their
 
content.
